  ('disabled-f29af906-moex-00045', 'disabled-f29af906', 'disabled-f29af906-moex-110-7927631a', 'sub-disabled-f29af906-01', NULL, 'essay', '都市的蔓延常造成無計畫或蛙躍式發展，各國為管控此等現象，通常可採
智慧型成長原則（smart growth principles）進行規劃。試就智慧型成長之
主要原則以及可採行之工具，至少舉五例說明之。（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4e2253587098", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "406", "s": "1202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "土地利用概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "地政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-f29af906-moex-00046', 'disabled-f29af906', 'disabled-f29af906-moex-110-7927631a', 'sub-disabled-f29af906-01', NULL, 'essay', '按全國國土計畫法之規定，農業發展地區分類之劃設原則、土地使用原則
